过夜庇护所；临时休息场所

bilingual.source: Fans queued overnight to buy the latest smartphone.
bilingual.target: 粉丝们通宵排队购买最新的智能手机。

bilingual.source: The game was so hyped that fans lined up overnight.
bilingual.target: 这场比赛非常受期待，粉丝们通宵排队。

bilingual.source: The engineering team worked overnight to fix the problem.
bilingual.target: 工程学团队通宵工作来解决这个问题。

bilingual.source: Once, while working overnight at a store, he let a homeless man sleep in his truck.
bilingual.target: 有一次，他在一家商店通宵工作时，让一个流浪汉睡在他的卡车里。

bilingual.source: I've fostered cats overnight when it was necessary.
bilingual.target: 我已经树立了猫通宵时，它是必要的。

bilingual.source: After an overnight fast a sample of blood is taken.
bilingual.target: 经过一通宵的快速样本的血液是采取。

bilingual.source: That paper led him to develop an overnight shipping company.
bilingual.target: 这篇论文也最终引导他创办了一家通宵航运公司。

bilingual.source: An overnight party of girls who dress in nightclothes and and pass the night talking.
bilingual.target: 年轻姑娘穿着睡衣通宵闲谈的聚会。

bilingual.source: The government aims to provide designated overnight parking sites for these cylinder wagons.
bilingual.target: 政府计划为这些石油气瓶车提供指定的通宵停泊地点.

bilingual.source: That night but was soft and call him out and play all night, he disregards family feeling, in the middle of the night quietly ran out, with a soft one overnight.
bilingual.target: 但恰巧那晚柔又叫他出来玩通宵，于是他不顾家人的感受，半夜的时候悄悄跑了出来，陪了柔一个通宵。

list.abstract: 隔夜，就是指某些物品过夜的意思。如金融领域的保证金交易，隔夜后会影响资金结算。还有平常我们吃的菜，有些是不能吃的，生活中是需要注意的。

yingyinNormal.en: Like my dough, this could even be done overnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 就像我的面团一样，甚至可能花费一晚上来做。

yingyinNormal.en: Lobsters overnight? Oh, you're kidding. Let me see.
yingyinNormal.zh: 龙虾隔天就能送来？开什么玩笑，我看看。

yingyinNormal.en: Got eyes on him, Finch. As do I. Our new number has become infamous overnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看到他了，芬奇。我也是，我们的新号码一夜之间声名狼藉。

yingyinNormal.en: They say, if you stick a broom handle into the soil, it will flower overnight!
yingyinNormal.zh: 人们说，只要把一支扫把插进泥土，隔夜就会开出花。

yingyinNormal.en: Why not? With online shopping and overnight delivery, I can get anything I want.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么不能？有网上购物和隔天送达，我要什么有什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Really get a bit of tension in there and that whole thing goes in the fridge overnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 用保鲜膜裹紧了，把这些放在冰箱里一夜。

yingyinNormal.en: No seriously, you know the contracts I gave you, did you overnight them? What contracts?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有没有快递寄出我拿给你的合约？什么合约？

yingyinNormal.en: God, I'm really sorry. My issues are not gonna go away overnight, Toby. Well, neither am I.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，我实在很抱歉。我的烦恼不会一夜之间烟消云散，托比。好吧。我也不会。

yingyinNormal.en: If it's possible, I'd love to have my uniform dry-cleaned overnight. It's the only clothing that I have.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果可以，今晚你们把我的制服拿去干洗一下吧，我就只有这身衣服。

yingyinNormal.en: And the much longer and profound erosion of middle-class jobs and incomes isn't something we're going to reverse overnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 更长时间和更深刻地对中产阶层就业岗位和收入的侵蚀，我们并不能在一夜之间改变它们。

yingyinNormal.en: I am sure that the parents have gone through a lot, too. Sure. You just don't get comfortable with something like that overnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他父母肯定也经历了很多困难。当然，那种事不可能是一下子就能接受的。

yingyinNormal.en: Like, okay, this one girl, Kathy Geiger, got really good grades, so we blindfolded her, tied her up and left her in a cornfield overnight.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如有个女生，凯西·盖格考试经常得高分，于是我们蒙上她的眼睛，把她五花大绑到玉米地，留她在那过夜。

yingyinNormal.en: If we hired them, they dropped straight out of college overnight and spent whatever allowance they had on a new suit from our Stratton tailor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只要我们一聘用 他们便立刻辍学，然后花光自己的零用钱从我们斯奥御用裁缝那定新西装。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you know how much it costs to pack a tuna fish sandwich in dry ice and overnight it from Texas? Well, I do, and my mother says it's too expensive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道从德州连夜寄来干冰包装的金枪鱼三明治要多贵吗？反正我知道，我妈说太贵了。

yingyinNormal.en: Of course not. And technically, magic beans would be food. Although eating them would be quite a waste, since you could plant them, and overnight, have a giant beanstalk, which would provide enough roughage for a small city.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然没有。况且严格来说，魔豆也是食物，虽然吃了它们怪浪费的，因为你可以种植它们，然后一夜之间就会长成一株巨大的豆茎，足够一个小城市吃的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
